VIn another cave, we found a different type of microalgae.
p62
aVThis one is able to use ocean mist as a source of water,
p63
aVand strikingly lives in the very bottom of a cave,
p64
aVso it has adapted to live with less than 0.1 percent
p65
aVof the amount of light that regular plants need.
